<L>__{int shipyard day.}
<B>__{a small marina. through the open doors we see the marina beyond.}
<A>__{gleaming, molten metal is being poured into a small mould by a}
<B>__{workman.}
<A>__{joe moore, now without moustache and glasses, with light, greying hair, in a cheap sportcoat, comes over, and gives the workman a few}
<B>__{directions. the workman nods. camera takes moore past several}
<A>__{boats in the shed, in various stages of disassembly. out of the small shed, and to the pier of the marina, where we see fran tying up the sloop, and the florid man descending the gangplank.}
<C>__{moore}
<D>__{what do you think?}
<C>__{florid man}
<D>__{think you're too old for that girl how'd you ever get a girl like that...?}
