<D>__{no, i'm serious. what's a girl like hh...}
<C>__{moore}
<P>__{(shrugs)}
<D>__{she's got this "father" thing. you like the boat?}
<C>__{florid man}
<D>__{waal... your price is rather high...}
<C>__{moore}
<D>__{i will tell you what, then why'nt you go build one...}
